---
title: Roasted Lamb Shoulder & Mint Sauce with Parmesan Veggie Mash & Almonds
description: We’re dining with the couple of the century - lamb and mint sauce. There’s no beating them for compatibility when they come together on the plate, especially with a potato and leek mash on the side. Then again, those veggies sprinkled with almonds might be the next best thing. We’ll leave the judging up to you!

